RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT distinct a.contract_ref_no, b.user_ref_no, x.counterparty, x.CONTRACT_CCY, y.principal_outstanding_bal, z.short_name from oltb_contract_master a , oltbs_contract b, oltb_contract x ,oltb_contract_balance y , oltms_customer z where a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_reF_no and a.version_no = b.latest_version_no and x.counterparty = z.customer_no and b.branch = global.current_branch and b.contract_status = 'A'and b.auth_status = 'A'and b.module_code = 'LB' and x.contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no and x.contracT_status = 'A' and x.contract_ref_no = y.contract_ref_no and x.product_type = 'C' and exists (SELECT contract_ref_no FROM oltbs_contract_linkages l WHERE l.linked_to_ref = a.contract_ref_no AND l.linkage_valid='Y' AND l.linkage_type='C')AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR WHERE product_code = b.product_code AND branch_code = GLOBAL.current_branch AND user_id = GLOBAL.user_id)
select rate_code,rate_code_desc from LFTMS_STANDARD_RATE_CODE where rate_type='S'and record_stat='O'and auth_stat='A'

SELECT DISTINCT a.rate_code,b.field_desc FROM LFTMS_TREASURY_RATE_CODE a, OLTMS_STATIC_MAINTENANCE b WHERE a.rate_code = b.field_name AND a.auth_stat = 'A' AND a.record_stat = 'O'AND b.maintenance_type = 'RTCD' AND a.rate_code_usage = b.field_type ORDER BY a.rate_code

select a.PRODUCT_CODE, b.product_description from LBTBS_BORROWER_DRAWDOWN_PROD a,oltms_product b, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD c, OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR d where a.PRODUCT_CODE = b.product_code and a.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? and b.product_code = c.product and c.PARTICIPANT_PRODUCT is not NULL and b.product_code = d.product_code and d.branch_code = global.current_branch and d.user_id = global.user_id and a.version_no = (SELECT max(version_no) from LBTBS_BORROWER_DRAWDOWN_PROD where contract_Ref_no = ?) UNION select a.DD_PRODUCT_CODE, b.product_description from LBTBS_CONTRACT_BORR_DDPROD a, oltms_product b, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD c, OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR d where a.DD_PRODUCT_CODE = b.product_code and a.contract_ref_no = ? and a.version_no = (select latest_version_no from oltbs_contract where contract_ref_no =?)and b.product_code = c.product and c.PARTICIPANT_PRODUCT is not NULL and b.product_code = d.product_code and d.branch_code = global.current_branch and d.user_id = global.user_id and a.customer_no = ?

select a.ccy, b.ccy_name from lbtb_facility_ccy a,cytms_ccy_defn b, oltbs_contract c where a.ccy = b.ccy_code and a.CONTRACT_REF_NO IN (select syndication_ref_no from oltbs_contract_master where contract_ref_no = ? AND version_no = (select max(version_no) FROM oltbs_contract_master WHERE contract_ref_no = ?)) and a.contract_ref_no = c.contract_ref_no and a.version_no = c.Latest_version_no MINUS select a.ccy, b.ccy_name from LBTBS_BORROWER_CCY a, cytms_ccy_defn b, oltbs_contract c where a.ccy = b.ccy_code and a.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? and a.contract_ref_no = c.contract_ref_no and a.version_no = c.Latest_version_no and nvl(a.block_ccy,'N')='Y' AND A.CCY <> '*.*' order by ccy

select distinct a.counterparty customer_no,customer_name1 from oltbs_contract a,oltbs_contract_master b,oltm_customer c where a.contract_ref_no=b.contract_ref_no and a.latest_version_no=b.version_no and a.module_code='LB'and a.auth_status='A'and b.product_type='L'and a.contract_status='A' and b.tranche_ref_no=? and a.counterparty = c.customer_no and a.branch = global.current_branch

select a.contract_ref_no, a.user_ref_no, a.counterparty, c.PRINCIPAL_OUTSTANDING_BAL from oltbs_contract a, oltbs_contract_master b , OLTBS_CONTRACT_BALANCE c where a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no and a.latest_version_no = b.version_no and a.module_code = 'LB' and a.product_code = ? and a.counterparty = ? and a.contract_ccy = ? and a.auth_status = 'A' and b.product_type = 'L' and b.rollover_allowed = 'Y' and b.rollover_method= 'C' and b.maturity_date = ? and a.contract_status = 'A' and b.tranche_ref_no = ? AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = c.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND nvl(b.swing_line,'N')='N' AND nvl(b.Ancillary, 'N') = 'N' and NOT EXISTS (SELECT contract_ref_no FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLLOVER r WHERE r.contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no AND r.version_no = a.latest_version_no AND nvl(r.ROLL_INST_STATUS, 'X') IN ('I', 'P', 'C')) AND a.contract_ref_no not in (select a.child_ref_no from lbtbs_contract_consol_detail a, lbtbs_contract_consol_master b where a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no and b.rollover_status IN ('I', 'P', 'C')) AND a.branch = global.current_branch AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR WHERE product_code = a.product_code AND branch_code = GLOBAL.current_branch AND user_id = GLOBAL.user_id) AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT contract_ref_no FROM lbtbs_contract_payment_due WHERE contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no) AND NOT EXISTS ( Select 1 from LFTB_MARGIN_REVN_ACTIVATED_CONT mrg where mrg.contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no )

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT a.rate_code,b.field_desc FROM LFTMS_TREASURY_RATE_CODE a, OLTMS_STATIC_MAINTENANCE b WHERE a.rate_code = b.field_name and a.auth_stat = 'A' AND a.record_stat = 'O' AND b.maintenance_type = 'RTCD' AND a.rate_code_usage = b.field_type UNION select rate_code,rate_code_desc from lftms_standard_rate_code where rate_type='S' and record_stat='O' and auth_stat='A'

select distinct rate_code ,rate_descr from cftms_rate_code where branch_code = global.current_branch and record_stat = 'O' and auth_stat = 'A' UNION SELECT DISTINCT RATE_CODE, RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RFR_MASTER WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND TYPE = NVL(?,TYPE) ORDER BY RATE_CODE

SELECT RATE_CODE, RATE_CODE_DESC FROM (SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE AS RATE_CODE, B.FIELD_DESC AS RATE_CODE_DESC, A.AUTH_STAT AS AUTH_STAT, A.RECORD_STAT AS RECORD_STAT FROM LFTMS_TREASURY_RATE_CODE A, OLTMS_STATIC_MAINTENANCE B WHERE A.RATE_CODE = B.FIELD_NAME AND B.MAINTENANCE_TYPE = 'RTCD' AND A.RATE_CODE_USAGE = B.FIELD_TYPE UNION SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE AS RATE_CODE, A.RATE_DESCR AS RATE_CODE_DESC, A.AUTH_STAT AS AUTH_STAT, A.RECORD_STAT AS RECORD_STAT FROM CFTMS_RATE_CODE A, CFTMS_FLOAT_RATE_MASTER B WHERE A.RATE_CODE = B.RATE_CODE AND B.CCY_CODE = ? AND A.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND A.BRANCH_CODE = B.BRANCH_CODE UNION SELECT RATE_CODE, RATE_CODE_DESC, AUTH_STAT, RECORD_STAT FROM LFTMS_STANDARD_RATE_CODE WHERE RATE_TYPE = 'S') WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY RATE_CODE

SELECT a.FREQUENCY, a.RATE_CODE, a.units, a.CCY_CODE FROM LFTM_TENOR_CODE_MAINT a, lftm_rate_code_maint b WHERE a.RATE_CODE = ? AND a.CCY_CODE = ? and a.rate_code = b.rate_code and a.ccy_code = b.ccy_code and b.auth_stat = 'A'

select a.PRODUCT_CODE, b.product_description from LBTBS_BORROWER_DRAWDOWN_PROD a,oltms_product b, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD c, OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR d where a.PRODUCT_CODE = b.product_code and a.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? and b.product_code = c.product and c.PARTICIPANT_PRODUCT is not NULL and b.product_code = d.product_code and d.branch_code = global.current_branch and d.user_id = global.user_id and a.version_no = (SELECT max(version_no) from LBTBS_BORROWER_DRAWDOWN_PROD where contract_Ref_no = ?) UNION select a.DD_PRODUCT_CODE, b.product_description from LBTBS_CONTRACT_BORR_DDPROD a, oltms_product b, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD c, OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR d where a.DD_PRODUCT_CODE = b.product_code and a.contract_ref_no = ? and a.version_no = (select latest_version_no from oltbs_contract where contract_ref_no =?)and b.product_code = c.product and c.PARTICIPANT_PRODUCT is not NULL and b.product_code = d.product_code and d.branch_code = global.current_branch and d.user_id = global.user_id and a.customer_no = ?
